---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service - Interior Design" description="Terms of service governing the use of our interior design services and website.">
  <Navigation />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] bg-gradient-to-br from-espresso-900 via-espresso-950 to-espresso-900 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-72 h-72 bg-gold-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Terms and conditions governing our interior design services and client relationships.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <Section 
    title=""
    subtitle=""
    className="py-20 bg-white"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg prose-slate">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-center mb-0">
          <strong>Last Updated:</strong> September 2025
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        By accessing and using this website and our interior design services, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by the above, please do not use this service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We provide comprehensive interior design services including but not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
              <li>Residential interior design</li>
              <li>Commercial interior design</li>
              <li>Space planning and layout design</li>
              <li>Design consultation and styling</li>
              <li>Custom furniture and millwork design</li>
              <li>Project management and coordination</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">3. Client Responsibilities</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        As a client, you agree to:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Provide accurate and complete information about your space, needs, and preferences</li>
        <li>• Notify us promptly of any material changes in your project requirements</li>
        <li>• Review and approve design proposals in a timely manner</li>
        <li>• Pay all fees and charges as agreed upon in the design agreement</li>
        <li>• Provide access to the project site as needed for design work</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">4. Design Services</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Our interior design services are provided in accordance with professional design standards and best practices. We will:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Act in your best interests and respect your design vision</li>
        <li>• Provide suitable design recommendations based on your style, needs, and budget</li>
        <li>• Disclose all material information about vendors, contractors, and costs</li>
        <li>• Maintain appropriate records of all design work and communications</li>
        <li>• Provide regular project updates and design presentations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">5. Fees and Compensation</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Our fee structure will be disclosed in your design agreement. Fees may include:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>• Design fees based on project scope and complexity</li>
        <li>• Consultation fees for initial design meetings</li>
        <li>• Project management fees for coordination and oversight</li>
        <li>• Vendor and contractor coordination fees</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        All fees will be clearly disclosed before services are provided and will be detailed in your design agreement.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">6. Project Considerations</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Interior design projects involve various considerations and potential challenges. You should be aware of the following:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Timeline variations - projects may experience delays due to material availability, contractor schedules, or unforeseen conditions</li>
        <li>• Budget considerations - costs may vary based on material selections, market conditions, and project scope changes</li>
        <li>• Design subjectivity - aesthetic preferences are personal and may evolve during the design process</li>
        <li>• Third-party dependencies - project success depends on reliable vendors, contractors, and suppliers</li>
        <li>• Space constraints - existing conditions may limit design options or require additional work</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">7. Confidentiality and Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We maintain strict confidentiality regarding your personal information and project details. Our privacy practices are detailed in our Privacy Policy, which complies with applicable privacy laws including GDPR 2025 and North American privacy regulations.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We will not disclose your information to third parties except as required by law or as necessary to provide our services.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, our liability for any claims arising from our services shall be limited to the amount of fees paid by you for the specific service giving rise to the claim. We shall not be liable for:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>
        <li>• Loss of profits or business opportunities</li>
        <li>• Delays or issues caused by third-party vendors, contractors, or suppliers</li>
        <li>• Material availability or cost fluctuations beyond our control</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">9. Termination</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Either party may terminate this agreement with written notice. Upon termination:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• All outstanding fees must be paid</li>
        <li>• We will provide final project documentation and design files</li>
        <li>• Confidentiality obligations continue indefinitely</li>
        <li>• You retain ownership of design concepts developed specifically for your project</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">10. Professional Standards</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We are committed to maintaining professional standards and compliance with all applicable laws and regulations, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Building codes and safety regulations</li>
        <li>• Professional design association standards</li>
        <li>• State and local business licensing requirements</li>
        <li>• Environmental and sustainability regulations</li>
        <li>• Consumer protection laws</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">11. Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Any disputes arising from these terms or our services shall be resolved through binding arbitration in accordance with the rules of the American Arbitration Association. The arbitration shall be conducted in the jurisdiction where our principal office is located.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">12. Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the state where our principal office is located, without regard to conflict of law principles.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">13. Modifications</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Material changes will be communicated to clients with at least 30 days' notice. Continued use of our services after such modifications constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-espresso-900 mb-6">14. Contact Information</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> info@espressodesignhouse.com</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-2"><strong>Phone:</strong> (+1) 555-0123</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600"><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Design District, New York, NY 10004</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 text-center">
          This Terms of Service is effective as of September 2025 and applies to all users of this website and our services.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

